Subject: Re: [T2] sealant between cylinder and case?

For sealing, I've used Loctite/Permatext Form-a-gasket #3H for the past 30
years.  Works for me.  Little bottle with a brush applicator.  Prolly gonna
need to use an old paint scraper to carefully remove the silicone off
though.
